==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Occasionally
<hw>Oc*ca"sion*al*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an
occasional manner; on occasion; at times, as convenience requires or
opportunity offers; not regularly.</def> <rj><au>Stewart.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The one, <persfn>Wolsey</persfn>, directly his subject by birth;
the other, his subject <qex>occasionally</qex> by his preferment.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Occasionate</ent>⟦br⟧
